      • findOne

        se.inera.axel.shs.xml.agreement.ShsAgreement findOne(String agreementId)
        Finds an agreement with the given id. Only local agreements are returned.
        Parameters:
        agreementId - the UUID of the agreement to find.
        Returns:
        the found agreement or null if no agreement was found.

      • findAgreements

        List<se.inera.axel.shs.xml.agreement.ShsAgreement> findAgreements(se.inera.axel.shs.xml.label.ShsLabel label)
        Finds all agreements that match the label. Looks for public agreements if no matching local agreement is found.
        Parameters:
        label - the label for which matching agreements should be found.
        Returns:
        a list of matching agreements or an empty list if no matching agreement was found.
